N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 63.8 - Circulars and price lists

State Regulations
A wholesale liquor licensee, a wholesale wine licensee
and a winery licensee having the right to sell wine at retail may circularize
and send price lists to persons to whom they are authorized to sell wine at
retail. Notes
